esource/Obesity\"}, {\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999761394068, \"rank\": 2.3860493777250077e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blasphemous mockery\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, drag queens played all the parts in this odious spectacle.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"all the parts\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"this odious spectacle\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No diversity at all.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No diversity\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not a single heterosexual.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not a single heterosexual\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, the \\\"fact checkers\\\" responded to the massive outrage over this by claiming that it was meant to depict an ancient festival honoring the Greek god Dionysus.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9980794349584863, \"rank\": 0.0015333954681041784, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5482165106062428e-34, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"fact checkers\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the massive outrage\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"an ancient festival\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure Dionysus would be honored to know he was portrayed by a drag queen.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5482165106062428e-34, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drag queen\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who can critically think understand perfectly well who and what they were mocking.\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus Christ is theonlyreligious figure and Christianity is theonlyfaith that can be openly mocked in America 2.0.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999761394068, \"rank\": 2.3860493777250077e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 2712, \"end\": 2724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999999572537, \"rank\": 4.2528294516985684e-11, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\"