with its theme of utter gayness, brought back memories of the 2012 opening ceremonies in London.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999599822, \"rank\": 4.032694500089244e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"its theme\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"utter gayness\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"memories\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, the one with all those hospital beds.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all those hospital beds\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They trotted out some 300 of these beds, in what we were told was a tribute to the NHS.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.792863267519704e-13, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these beds\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not realize that hospitals, sickness, or the NHS, had anything whatsoever to do with international sports.\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3234, \"end\": 3237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.792863267519704e-13, \"text\": \"NHS\",